    "main_content": "SkinSignal's Product Comparison Tool allows users to compare two skincare products face to face. The tool can compare two products, a product and ingredient list, or two ingredient lists. Users can manually paste two ingredient lists to see the results. The service is completely free with no registration required and no usage limits. Recent comparisons include various skincare products like sunscreens, toners, serums, eye creams, and body lotions from brands such as Tizo, Elta MD, Kiehl's, Pyunkang Yul, Beauty Of Joseon, Some By Mi, and Vaseline.",
